<template>

  {{ users }}
</template>
<script>
import axios from "axios";
export default {
  data(){
users:""
  },
  mounted() {
    this.fetchUsers();
  },
  methods: {
    async fetchUsers() {
      try {
        const res = await axios.get("http://localhost:4000/api/users");
        this.users = res.data.users;
        console.log(this.users)
      } catch (error) {
        console.error("Error fetching users:", error);
      }
    },
  },
};
</script>
